Class Repeat

  • java.lang.Object
    • music.Repeat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChordSequence

    public final class Repeat
extends java.lang.Object
implements ChordSequence
    The class Repeat represents a section of music with a repeat, and possibly alternate endings.
